c: 7
v: 33
t: "Vuga uti \"Mu by’ukuri, Nyagasani wanjye yaziririje ibikorwa by’urukozasoni, byaba ibikozwe ku mugaragaro cyangwa mu ibanga, ndetse n’ibyaha (ibyo ari byo byose), ibikorwa by’ubugome, no kubangikanya Allah n’ibyo atabahereye gihamya (ko bigomba gusengwa), no guhimbira Allah ibyo mutazi"